whether or not she's being truthful.

18:39.952 --> 18:43.404
You just be her lawyer
and only, and third…

18:44.213 --> 18:46.423
Stop hitting on her.

18:52.453 --> 18:53.997
Hey, Brad.

18:53.997 --> 18:55.545
All together now.

18:55.545 --> 18:57.355
Lesbian.

18:59.492 --> 19:00.928
Boys…

19:00.928 --> 19:02.203
how's our trial going?

19:02.203 --> 19:05.088
You think I'm just gonna wither
up and die in there, don't you?

19:05.088 --> 19:08.050
All these references
to our sex life, Denny.

19:08.050 --> 19:09.365
