19:09.365 --> 19:11.149
Please, since he can't recall.

19:11.149 --> 19:12.104
He's been amazing.

19:12.104 --> 19:14.684
I'd say we have 
a better-than-even chance.

19:17.559 --> 19:18.472
Hello.

19:18.472 --> 19:20.323
Hello.

19:21.173 --> 19:23.545
