19:43.244 --> 19:45.104
The firm is safe from ridicule.

19:49.765 --> 19:51.557
What did she want?

19:52.409 --> 19:54.113
Make sure I'm competent?

19:54.113 --> 19:56.359
Something like that.

19:56.654 --> 19:58.320
You were more than competent
today, Denny.

19:58.320 --> 20:00.330
–You were good, very good.
–I know.

20:00.330 --> 20:03.659
We must be doing our 
crosswords these days.

20:04.669 --> 20:07.668
Did she ask you to backstop me?

20:07.668 --> 20:09.373
