anything but amused.

30:53.024 --> 30:54.704
–I'm not..
–No, I, I got it.

30:54.948 --> 30:56.564
We'll split it.

30:57.307 --> 30:58.719
You go first.

30:59.050 --> 31:00.138
Fine.

31:02.523 --> 31:05.149
Okay, first, this big deal
about FDA approval…

31:05.149 --> 31:10.902
doctors prescribe medications every day
for uses the FDA never considered.

31:10.902 --> 31:15.198
