No government or, 
or court is gonna tell me,

34:38.033 --> 34:42.770
order me to 
continue losing my mind.

34:45.253 --> 34:47.289
I agree with the prosecutor.

34:47.289 --> 34:55.641
His claim that desperate people
will try desperate measures.

34:59.662 --> 35:02.162
So what?

35:43.872 --> 35:46.126
–Members of the jury,
