35:51.791 --> 35:55.245
In the matter of the commonwealth
of Massachusetts vs. Dr Robert Mclean…

35:55.245 --> 35:59.881
we the jury find in favor
of the defendant.

36:00.084 --> 36:02.969
We find the defendant
Dr Robert Mclean

36:02.969 --> 36:04.769
not guilty.

36:04.769 --> 36:07.368
Ladies and gentlemen of the jury,
I want to thank you for your service.

36:07.368 --> 36:09.408
At this time, you are dismissed.

36:09.408 --> 36:10.960
Court adjourned.

36:21.808 --> 36:24.219
So did she say anything after?

36:24.319 --> 36:27.654
She just shot me a look when
she was leaving the courthouse.

36:27.654 --> 36:28.748
She'll get over it.

36:28.748 --> 36:29.907
Yeah, I bet she will.

36:29.907 --> 36:32.394
Who knows? Maybe we'll even
get back together one day.

36:32.394 --> 36:34.497
Wouldn't be surprised.

36:35.675 --> 36:39.281
So why did you want 
to have dinner, Brad?

36:39.531 --> 36:41.663
To celebrate the victory or, uh…

36:41.663 --> 36:44.012
take one last shot at conversion?

36:49.060 --> 36:52.812
I wanted to have 
dinner to apologize.

36:53.992 --> 36:56.048
I did a really…

36:56.048 --> 36:58.523
terrible thing.

36:58.788 --> 37:01.986
I hired a private investigator
to follow you.

37:01.986 --> 37:05.811
I wanted to satisfy myself
that you were really gay,

37:06.434 --> 37:09.111
and I'm quite satisfied now.

37:11.999 --> 37:17.671
You went to see Stephanie
around midnight last night.

37:17.960 --> 37:20.086
Why would you do that?

37:23.300 --> 37:26.575
Well, had it half right.
Didn't I?

37:26.575 --> 37:29.525
You know, thinking Stephanie
sued you for…

37:29.525 --> 37:31.537
the publicity.

37:32.417 --> 37:34.540
You were both in on it.

37:34.906 --> 37:37.898
It girls or split girls…

37:38.627 --> 37:42.107
however you make the news,
you two are a really good team.

37:43.890 --> 37:46.810
Because I knew 
I was being deceived.

37:46.810 --> 37:49.488
I just wasn't sure how.

37:53.388 --> 37:57.940
I didn't plan for you to fall for me.

37:58.481 --> 38:01.122
Well, don't flatter yourself.

38:03.932 --> 38:06.046
I think that I should leave.

38:06.046 --> 38:07.694
No, no, you don't have to.
We won the case.

38:07.694 --> 38:09.944
Come on, this is a celebration.

38:11.744 --> 38:13.659
I'm gonna leave.

38:13.659 --> 38:15.801
Thank you, Brad.

38:17.126 --> 38:20.315
Um, and again,

38:20.584 --> 38:23.310
I'm sorry if…

38:27.721 --> 38:29.298
Thank you.

39:05.595 --> 39:07.511
That drug you're taking 
is an amphetamine

39:07.511 --> 39:11.464
with a dangerously high potential
