39:19.843 --> 39:22.954
You'll no doubt work like a demon.

39:22.954 --> 39:26.375
But certain pleasures will be gone.

39:26.511 --> 39:28.433
Like?

39:28.852 --> 39:31.442
Perhaps fishing…

39:31.442 --> 39:37.055
perhaps sitting in a chair
enjoying a football game…

39:37.215 --> 39:40.226
standing on a balcony…

39:40.226 --> 39:44.109
appreciating the quiet
joy of a friendship.

39:46.446 --> 39:49.823
There's more to life than 
recognizing faces, Denny.

39:49.823 --> 39:51.954
You prefer me in my fog?

39:51.954 --> 39:54.019
I prefer you.

39:55.192 --> 39:59.127
Your perspective and your humor,

39:59.127 --> 40:02.978
the acceptance and humility which…

40:02.978 --> 40:05.880
perhaps can only come with age.

40:08.341 --> 40:10.729
I prefer you.

40:19.135 --> 40:21.503
I've stopped taking the drug.

40:22.672 --> 40:25.537
I kind of like my fog, too.

40:26.906 --> 40:29.892
There's a certain license
that goes with it.

40:29.892 --> 40:33.344
Plus, I've said this before,
and I'll say it again.

40:33.438 --> 40:35.414
The answers in life…

40:35.414 --> 40:38.205
you don't find them here.

40:40.247 --> 40:44.017
First you look to god…

40:44.402 --> 40:47.950
and then…

40:49.200 --> 40:50.820
Fox news.

40:50.820 --> 40:52.756
Damn right.

40:54.124 --> 40:56.710
You Democrats.

40:57.017 --> 40:59.268
You Republicans.

